            "value": "Steps to reproduce\r\n\r\n1 - user an error hander and use an error controller\r\n2 - have an exception thrown during dispatching (unknown controller)\r\n3 - error handler controller renders its message in the layout\r\n4 - have a second exception get thrown ( eg wrong routes applied to a url view helper in the layout it is trying to render to)\r\n\r\nProblem:\r\nsuppresses all errors & exceptions!!!\r\n\r\nSee attached patch"
